This paper deals with a specific type of problem in MapReduce applications, which involves discovering relationships between pairs of inputs. This problem is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science, including data structures (cs.DS), databases (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), and distributed computing (cs.DC).
